information: since 1978, toppy srl designs and manufactures pile turners for the paper and processing industries. ongoing research and development have led the toppy pile turners to become the world leaders in the graphic and paper industries. our continuous growth led toppy’s management to create a dedicated department with highly qualified staff to best meet the continuous and growing requests coming from the packaging market. the new generation of toppy packaging pile turners aligns perfectly with the needs of the printing and processing world due to its speed and precision. toppy packaging also offers solutions to manage plastic pallets supplied by the main machine manufacturers in the packaging industry. toppy offers different pile turner solutions, each with different characteristics to adapt to multiple needs originating from the packaging industry, offering both stand-alone machines and machines integrated in existing lines. our experience in designing integrated and service logistics systems for the main printing and processing machines allows toppy to offer solutions to create all that is needed to handle loads on pallets in new plants, from paper warehouses to pile turners capable or automatically replacing the wooden pallet with a plastic pallet, up to production machines. toppy packaging is a essential partner for the paper and processing industry needs.

information: kemiplast manufactures high-performance flexible packaging for fast-moving consumer goods for both food and non-food categories. we are brc certified and specialized in printing and laminated biofilm, sustainable film & paper. our range of compostable and biodegradable film is continuously growing. our proactive customer orientation has helped us to anticipate market trends and thus we invest into innovative projects at early stages. these investments led to kemiplast’s most successful new product launches of bellavista®, belvedere® and natura bio system®. we sell to customers in more than twenty countries with focus on consumer goods categories such as fresh food, frozen food, bakery, consumer tissue & personal care and retail solutions. our customers choose kemiplast as their packaging partner because we consistently deliver high-quality flexible packaging material and best-in-class service level & support, while being committed to strategic innovation and efficiency programs. we highlight the importance of highly motivated, experienced personnel in driving our success, and give our people hands-on responsibility for their work and the tools to achieve their targets. enthusiastic, committed teams form an integral part of our overall commitment to continuous improvement and performing at our best.
